<p>
The DIAS Connected Home Platform is an integrated framework for broadband and triple play CPE that enables the seamless delivery of a wide range of service applications into the home with the need for separate systems. It is pre-integrated in Portus DIAS Gateways and may also be licensed to run in other vendor gateways.
</p>
<p>
Portus has developed a range of key DIAS Applications, ranging from Home Monitoring, Home Security, and Home Messaging, to Home Metering and Home Control, ready to be deployed to the platform by the operator.
</p>
<p>
All applications run on the DIAS Connected Home Platform and are controlled through a sophisticated, intuitive, user interface that can be accessed through a browser on any device from wall panel, tablet, PC or PDA to advanced mobile phone, either inside the premises, or remotely.
</p>
<p>
The DIAS Platform is a secure framework that will guarantee the security, integrity and privacy of service provider data, customer data and video streams.
</p>